@startuml sdk-bridge-resume-recovery-flow

title sdk-bridge resume / recovery — sendMessage 主路径 + recoverAndSend 单飞 + jsonl-missing fallback (双端)

actor Caller as C
participant "sdk-bridge\n(index.ts)" as SB
participant "sessions Map\n(in-memory)" as SMap
participant "recoverer.ts\nrecoverAndSend" as Rec
participant "sessionRepo (DB)" as DB
participant "sessionManager" as SM
participant "SDK subprocess\n(claude-code / codex-cli)" as SDK
participant "stream-processor (claude)\nthread-loop (codex)" as Stream
participant "fs (~/.claude/projects)" as Fs

== 主路径: sendMessage in-memory active ==

C -> SB: sendMessage(sessionId, text)
SB -> SMap: sessions.has(sessionId)?

alt sessions.has === true (主路径)
  SMap --> SB: internal { permissionResponder, inputStream, ... }
  SB -> Stream: pushUserMessage(text)
  Stream -> SDK: stdin write 'user' input
  SDK -> Stream: 'assistant' / 'user' / 'result' messages
  Stream -> SMap: parseAndEmit (advance state)
  SMap --> C: emit AgentEvent (kind: 'message' / 'status' / 'file-changed')
else sessions.has === false (断连)
  SMap --> SB: undefined
  SB -> Rec: recoverAndSend(sessionId, text)
end

== 断连自愈: recoverAndSend (single-flight 锁) ==

Rec -> Rec: recovering.set(sessionId, promise)\n(防同 sessionId 并发 sendMessage 双 createSession)
note right of Rec
  REVIEW_60 R1 codex MED-1 修法:
  unarchive + 占位 message dedup 从 IIFE 外移到 IIFE 内
  recovering.set 同步注册防 archived session 并发
  sendMessage 双 createSession 破坏不变量
end note

Rec -> DB: sessionRepo.get(sessionId) → cwd / permissionMode / lifecycle / archived_at
alt row null → reject
  Rec --> C: error "session-not-found"
end

Rec -> DB: sessionRepo.unarchive (archived_at = null)
note right of DB
  R1 fix: archived session 自愈 unarchive
  恢复对话身份连续性
end note

Rec -> SMap: emit 占位 message '⚠ SDK 通道已断开,正在自动恢复…'\n(非 error 占位,UI 不显示哑巴 busy)

== cwd 启发式 fallback (recoverer.ts:103-220) ==

Rec -> Fs: cwdExists(row.cwd)?
alt cwd 已失效 (worktree 被 archive_plan 删 / 跨设备同步丢)
  Rec -> Rec: 启发式找仍存在的祖先目录\n(走 worktree path 取段之前 / 父目录 walk 不超过 home)
  alt 找到 fallback cwd
    Rec -> SMap: emit info '⚠ cwd 失效,自动回退到 <fallback-cwd>'
  else 找不到
    Rec -> SMap: emit error '⚠ cwd 失效且无法回退'
    Rec --> C: reject
  end
end

== jsonl-missing fallback (CLI 隐式 fork 第二种边界) ==

Rec -> Fs: jsonl 路径 exists? (~/.claude/projects/<encoded-cwd>/<sessionId>.jsonl)
alt jsonl 不存在 (CLI --resume <sid> 撞 "No conversation found")
  note right of Rec
    REVIEW_60 R2 reviewer-claude HIGH 修法:
    claude createSession catch 双 key 清理 sessions Map
    (sessions.delete(applicationSid) + sessions.delete(tempKey))
    防 sessions.set 切 applicationSid 后 catch 残留 leak
  end note
  Rec -> SB: maybeJsonlFallback (不带 resume 走新建 createSession)
  SB -> SDK: createSession(opts) 无 resume
  SDK --> SB: newRealSessionId (fresh thread)
  SB -> SM: renameSdkSession(OLD_SID, newRealSessionId)\n(应用层 events/file_changes/summaries 子表整体迁移)
  SB -> SMap: sessions.set(newRealSessionId, internal)
  alt claude jsonl-fallback prepend LLM 摘要
    Rec -> Rec: 拼接 history 摘要 prepend 到首条 prompt
  end
end

== 正常 resume (jsonl 存在 + cwd valid) ==

alt jsonl exists + cwd valid
  Rec -> SB: createSession({resume: sessionId, prompt: text, cwd, permissionMode})
  SB -> SDK: createSession(opts) 带 --resume
  SDK -> Fs: read jsonl 复原历史
  SDK --> SB: realSessionId (first realId 拿到)

  alt realId !== opts.resume (CLI 软 fork)
    SB -> SM: releaseSdkClaim(OLD_ID)
    SB -> SM: renameSdkSession(OLD_ID, realId)\n(DB record + 子表整体迁移)
  end

  SB -> SMap: sessions.set(realId, internal)
end

== 收尾: 把 text 通过主路径 push ==

Rec -> SB: 回到主路径 sendMessage(text)\n(后续等待者通过 inflight Promise 完成后重新走完整 sendMessage)
SB -> Stream: pushUserMessage(text)
Stream -> SDK: stdin write
SDK -> Stream: response messages
Stream -> SMap: emit AgentEvent

Rec -> Rec: recovering.delete(sessionId) finally\n(REVIEW_60 R3 修法: await 前窗口 finally 单飞锁)

@enduml
